rying out the vote in parliament.<ref>[http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/japan-brawl-erupts-parliament-over-approval-controversial-security-bills-video-1520101 Japan: Brawl erupts in parliament over approval of controversial security bills &#91;Video&#93;]</ref>\n\n== Jordan ==\nThere has been violence during [[Parliament of Jordan]] sessions, including one instance where a member was removed from the building after he fired an AK-47 from the hall at a fellow member of parliament.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/jordan/9916332/Scuffle-breaks-out-in-Jordanian-parliament.html|title=Scuffle breaks out in Jordanian parliament|last=Mar 2013|first=6:00PM GMT 07|date=2013-03-07|website=The Daily Telegraph|access-date=2019-02-07}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/jordan/10303043/MP-fires-AK-47-during-parliament-session-in-Jordan.html|title=MP fires AK-47 during parliament session in Jordan|last=Sep 2013|first=11:00AM BST 12|date=2013-09-12|website=The Daily Telegraph|access-date=2019-02-07}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.latimes.com/world/middleeast/la-fg-jordan-parliament-sit-down-20141208-story.html|title=Fracas in Jordan's parliament leads to 'Sit down' campaign}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.middleeasteye.net/news/chaos-erupts-jordan-parliament-over-former-egyptian-president-morsi-1834768921|title=Chaos erupts in Jordan parliament over clashing Morsi aid claims}}</ref><ref>{{in lang|ar}} [https://arabic.rt.com/middle_east/999562-%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%A7%D8%AC%D8%B1%D8%A9-%D9%81%D9%8A-%D9%85%D8%AC%D9%84%D8%B3-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%86%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%A8-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D8%B1%D8%AF%D9%86%D9%8A-%D9%88%D8%B6%D8%B1%D8%A8-%D8%A8%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%80%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B9%D9%82%D8%A7%D9%84/# \"\u0645\u0634\u0627\u062c\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u064a \u0645\u062c\u0644\u0633 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u0631\u062f\u0646\u064a \u0648\u0636\u0631\u0628 \u0628\u0627\u0644\u0640\"\u0627\